*Galax urceolata* (Poir.) Brummitt
det. Michelle L. Gaynor (FLAS)          2024

PLANTS OF SOUTH CAROLINA
CHEROKEE COUNTY

*GALAX APHYLLA* L.

Leaves tough, glossy; abundant in
patches or large clumps; slopes with
*Kalmia latifolia*, *Oxydendrum*, oaks and
hickories; E side of S-209, about 0.5
mi SE of prominent monadnock and on
W side of Bells Branch; SSE of Blacksburg.

John B. Nelson 5185          17 March 1987
